(1, 'Cetaphil Daily Gentle Skin Cleanser Face Wash (500ml)', 'A range of skin care products from Galderma laboratories, Cetaphil skincare line include bar soaps, cleansers, creams, lotions and moisturizers\r\nHelps to effectively remove dirt, excess oils and makeup without drying out the skin.\r\nIt may help reduce the appearance of pores for smoother-looking skin.\r\nHelps strengthen the skin’s moisture barrier.\r\nSoothes and replenishes skin’s moisture\r\nNon-comedogenic and pH-balanced. \r\nIt doesn’t irritate the skin.\r\nCustomers also bought', 969.43, 'Personal Care', 2, 'Cetaphil_1.jpg', '2025-11-09 03:28:09', 'Skin Care', 'Galderma India Pvt. Ltd', 1031.31, 6, '[\"Gently cleanses the skin.\\r\",\"Soothes the skin.\\r\",\"Keeps the skin moisturised and healthy.\\r\",\"Moisturises without leaving residue that can clog pores.\\r\",\"Maintains the natural pH balance of the skin.\"]', 'All Other Combinations (0 Mg)', 'Supports Gentle Cleansing: Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser provides a thorough cleansing experience without relying on harsh ingredients or abrasive agents. It helps remove dirt, oil and impurities from the skin’s surface while preserving the skin\'s natural oils. This makes it ideal for daily use, especially for those with sensitive or dry skin who need a gentle yet effective cleansing solution.\r\n \r\nHelps Hydrate the Skin: The inclusion of glycerin and panthenol in the formula helps ensure that the skin remains well-hydrated during and after cleansing. These humectants help draw moisture from the environment and help lock in moisture and support the skin’s natural hydration processes. This dual action helps reduce dryness and keeps the skin soft and supple.\r\n \r\nHelps Soothe and Calm Irritated Skin: Enriched with panthenol and niacinamide, Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser offers soothing and calming benefits. Panthenol helps reduce inflammation and irritation, while niacinamide works to minimise redness and support the skin’s repair mechanisms. This combination is particularly beneficial for individuals with sensitive or reactive skin, providing relief from discomfort and promoting a more even skin tone.\r\n \r\nNon-Irritating Formula: Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser is formulated without harsh soaps or synthetic fragrances which can often cause irritation or allergic reactions. Its mild and non-irritating formula helps ensure that it is suitable for even the most sensitive skin types. This gentle approach helps reduce skin irritation and maintains a comfortable and balanced skin condition.\r\n \r\nHelps Maintain pH Balance: The cleanser’s formula includes citric acid which helps adjust and maintain the pH balance of the product to match that of the skin. This pH balance is crucial for preserving the skin’s natural acidity and overall health. By aligning with the skin’s natural pH, the cleanser helps avoid disruption of the skin barrier and supports optimal skin function.\r\n \r\nSuitable for All Skin Types: Designed to cater to a broad range of skin types, Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser is especially beneficial for those with dry, sensitive or combination skin. Its gentle formulation ensures that it cleanses effectively without stripping the skin of essential moisture.\r\n \r\nNon-Comedogenic: The cleanser is formulated to be non-comedogenic, meaning it does not clog pores. This is particularly important for individuals prone to acne or breakouts, as clogged pores can exacerbate these issues. By maintaining clear pores, Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser helps reduce acne and supports a clearer, healthier complexion.', 'Apply Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser to damp skin. \r\nGently massage in circular motions, then rinse thoroughly with lukewarm water. \r\nUse twice daily, morning and evening, to remove impurities and maintain hydrated, clean skin. Pat dry with a soft towel.', 'Read the label carefully before use.\r\nStore in a cool dry place. \r\nKeep away from direct sunlight and strong-smelling substances.\r\nKeep out of the reach of children.\r\nThe ideal temperature for storage is 30 degrees centigrade.', 'Good to Know:Paraben free;Lightweight and non-greasy;Gentle on Skin \r\nQuick Tips:Use Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser twice daily for optimal brightening and hydration;Massage the cleanser gently in circular motions to enhance blood circulation and product absorption;Follow with a moisturiser and sunscreen to lock in moisture and protect your brightened skin\r\nConcerns It Can Help With:Cleansing dirt, oil and impurities;Dry skin;Irritated skin', '[\"Can Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser be used on sensitive skin?:Yes, it is specifically designed for sensitive skin. Its gentle formula cleanses without irritation, making it suitable for even the most delicate skin types.\\r\",\"How often should I use this cleanser?:For best results, use Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser twice daily, once in the morning and once in the evening.\\r\",\"Is this cleanser suitable for acne-prone skin?:Yes, it is non-comedogenic and helps reduce clogged pores, making it suitable for acne-prone skin.\\r\",\"Does Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser contain fragrances?:No, it is free from synthetic fragrances, reducing the risk of irritation and making it ideal for sensitive skin.\\r\",\"Can I use this cleanser if I have eczema or rosacea?:Yes, the gentle formula is suitable for conditions like eczema and rosacea. It cleanses without causing additional irritation.\\r\",\"Is it necessary to use a toner after this cleanser?:It\\u2019s not necessary, but if you use a toner, choose one that complements your skin type and concerns. Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser provides a balanced pH which may reduce the need for additional products.\\r\",\"Can this cleanser be used with other skincare products?:Yes, it can be used with other skincare products. For best results, follow with a suitable moisturiser and any prescribed treatments or serums.\"]', 'Dr. Divya Mandia', 'Medical Content Writer | 9 years PhD in Chemistry', 'Dr. Mandeep Chadha', 'Lead Medical Content Reviewer | 11 years MBBS, DNB (OBGY)', 'Lotus Corporate Park, D Wing Unit 801802 Off Western Express Highway, Goregaon (East), Mumbai, Maharashtra 400063\n\nCountry of origin: INDIA\nExpiry on or after: March 2026\n\nIn case of any issues, contact us:\nsupport@medicare.com|06257814252\nAddress: 6th floor, Urmi Corporate Park Street, Atal Sharani Road, Kolkata 700054.', 'We, at Medicare make a diligent attempt to deliver accurate, expert- drafted and thoroughly reviewed medicine related information to our consumers. However, it should, by no means, be considered a substitute for prescription from a certified doctor or a trustworthy doctor-patient relationship. In fact we detest any form of self medication without expert advice. The sole purpose of the information on our portal is to educate our consumers, which helps improve the communication between a doctor and a patient. The information by no means is complete in its entirety and should not be used to diagnose or treat any medical condition. No amount of information can replace the experience and expertise of a doctor, therefore his/her advice always holds priority and should be followed appropriately.'),
