(3, 'Lice Clear Shampoo 50ml', 'is used to manage head lice by killing lice and their eggs. It works on the lice\'s nervous system, causing paralysis and death. Applied to dry hair, left for the suggested time, and rinsed, it’s followed by fine-toothed combing to remove dead lice and nits, helping reduce the risk of reinfestation effectively.', 49.17, 'Personal Care', 15, 'Lice_Clear_Shampoo_1.png', '2025-11-14 02:51:49', 'Hair Care', 'Leeford Healthcare', 75.64, 35, '[\"Eliminates lice and nits with a natural formulation.\\r\",\"Soothes the scalp with gentle herbal ingredients.\\r\",\"Protects hair from lice re-infestation.\\r\",\"Cleanses the hair thoroughly while maintaining scalp health.\\r\",\"Nourishes and strengthens hair with each wash.\\r\",\"Provides a refreshing and cooling sensation during application.\"]', 'Cinnamomum Camphora (0.05 %) + Citrus Medica(citron) (0.05 %) + Eucalyptus Oil (0.05 %) + Guladaudi (0.02 %) + Nimba Azadirachta Indica (0.1 %) + Seva (Pyrus Malus) (0.05 %) + Sitaphal (0.05 %) + Van Tulsi (Ocimum Basilicum) (0.08 %)', 'Removes Lice and Nits: Lice Clear Shampoo effectively targets and eliminates lice and nits from the scalp and hair. Its powerful blend of natural ingredients helps break the life cycle of lice, making it easier to manage infestations.\r\nSoothes the Scalp: The natural extracts in Lice Clear Shampoo, such as Neem and Camphor, provide a soothing effect on the scalp, reducing irritation, itchiness and redness caused by lice bites. This makes the process more comfortable.\r\nMaintains Scalp Health: Ingredients like Eucalyptus Oil and Neem help maintain a healthy scalp by reducing fungal and bacterial growth. Lice Clear Shampoo not only removes lice but also supports overall scalp health, making it suitable for regular use.\r\nManages Re-infestation: With insecticidal properties from herbs like Neem and Chrysanthemum, Lice Clear Shampoo helps in reducing the re-infestation of lice. Regular use creates an environment that is unfavourable for lice, ensuring longer-lasting results.\r\nNourishes and Cleanses Hair: Apart from its lice-removing properties, Lice Clear Shampoo nourishes the hair with herbal ingredients. It cleanses the scalp and hair thoroughly, leaving them refreshed without stripping natural oils.', 'Wet the hair and scalp thoroughly.\r\nApply an adequate amount of Lice Clear Shampoo to the scalp and hair.\r\nMassage gently to create a lather, focusing on the scalp area.\r\nLeave the shampoo on for about 5-10 minutes to allow the ingredients to work.\r\nRinse thoroughly with clean water.\r\nFor best results, use twice a week or as directed by a healthcare professional.', 'Read the label carefully before use.\r\nKeep it out of the reach of children.\r\nFor external use only.\r\nAvoid contact with eyes. \r\nIf irritation develops, discontinue use and consult your dermatologist.\r\nStore in a cool and dry place away from direct sunlight.', 'Good to Know:It is safe and gentle to use;It is formulated with an Ayurvedic formula;It is non-toxic\r\nQuick Tips:Use a fine-toothed comb after shampooing to remove dead lice and nits;Avoid sharing combs, hats or pillows during the whole procedure to reduce the spread of lice;Follow up with a conditioner for easier combing and detangling\r\nAllergy Information:It contains natural ingredients like Eucalyptus Oil and Neem;If you have known sensitivities to these ingredients, consult a healthcare professional before use\r\nConcerns It Can Help With:Lice infestations;Itchy and irritated scalp;Dry or flaky scalp due to lice', '[\"What is Lice Clear Shampoo used for?:Lice Clear Shampoo is used to eliminate head lice. It eliminates lice, removes their eggs (nits), and reduces itching on the scalp. With regular use, it helps keep the hair clean, healthy, and free from lice infestations.\\r\",\"Is Lice Clear Shampoo safe for children?:Yes, Lice Clear Shampoo is formulated with natural ingredients, making it safe for children. However, consult a healthcare professional if your child has sensitive skin or any allergies.\\r\",\"Can I use conditioner after applying Lice Clear Shampoo?:Yes, you can use a conditioner after rinsing out the shampoo to detangle hair and make it easier to comb out dead lice and nits.\\r\",\"Does Lice Clear Shampoo have any side effects?:Lice Clear Shampoo is made with natural ingredients and is generally well-tolerated. If you experience any irritation or allergic reaction, discontinue use and seek medical advice.\"]', 'Dr. Divya Mandial', 'Medical Content Writer | 9 years PhD in Chemistry', 'Dr. Mandeep Chadha', 'Lead Medical Content Reviewer | 11 years MBBS, DNB (OBGY)', 'Leo House, Shaheed Bhagat Singh Nagar, Dugri Dhandra Road, Near Joseph School Ludhiana PB 141002 IN\nCountry of origin: INDIA\nExpiry on or after: March 2026\n\nIn case of any issues, contact us:\nsupport@medicare.com|06257814252\nAddress: 6th floor, Urmi Corporate Park Street, Atal Sharani Road, Kolkata 700054.', 'We, at Medicare make a diligent attempt to deliver accurate, expert- drafted and thoroughly reviewed medicine related information to our consumers. However, it should, by no means, be considered a substitute for prescription from a certified doctor or a trustworthy doctor-patient relationship. In fact we detest any form of self medication without expert advice. The sole purpose of the information on our portal is to educate our consumers, which helps improve the communication between a doctor and a patient. The information by no means is complete in its entirety and should not be used to diagnose or treat any medical condition. No amount of information can replace the experience and expertise of a doctor, therefore his/her advice always holds priority and should be followed appropriately.'),
(4, 'Galact Elaichi Flavour Granules 400gm', 'Galact Elaichi Flavour Granules 400gm is used for supporting nursing mothers in enhancing their breast milk supply. It is a specially formulated lactation supplement infused with a delightful elaichi flavour. These granules help provide a palatable solution without the bitterness often associated with herbal supplements. The product is enriched with seven potent Ayurvedic herbs, each selected for its lactation-enhancing properties. This unique blend promotes the quantity of milk and improves its quality, ensuring optimal nourishment for the baby. Galact granules also function as a rejuvenator in the postnatal phase, helping mothers regain strength and balance after childbirth. Easy to use, these granules can be mixed with milk or water, making them a convenient addition to daily dietary habits. Galact Granules are a natural choice for mothers seeking to enhance their breastfeeding experience and bond with their newborns.', 629.21, 'Personal Care', 15, 'Galact-Elaichi-Flavour-Granules_1.jpeg', '2025-11-14 03:08:11', 'Baby And Mom Care', 'Emcure Pharmaceuticals Ltd', 679.81, 8, '[\"Supports lactation and breast milk production.\\r\",\"Contains a blend of seven Ayurvedic herbs for effective results.\\r\",\"Infused with a delicious elaichi (cardamom) flavour for a pleasant taste.\\r\",\"Acts as a general tonic and rejuvenator during the postnatal period.\\r\",\"Free from bitterness, it is easy to incorporate into daily routine.\\r\",\"Safe for breastfeeding mothers when used as directed.\"]', 'Chandrasura(lepidium Sativum) (1 Gm) + Cuminum Cyminum ( Spice Cumin ) (1 Gm) + Gokshura (2.5 Gm) + Shatavari Root Powder (15 Gm) + Sowa (1 Gm) + Vidarikand (1 Gm) + Yashtimadhu (1 Gm)', 'Milk Production: Galact Elaichi Flavour granules may help enhance breast milk quantity in nursing mothers by supporting natural lactation. This can promote better feeding and nourishment for the baby, helping in healthier growth and development during breastfeeding.\r\nMilk Quality: This granule might help improve the overall quality of breast milk by enriching it with essential nutrients. This could provide better nourishment to the baby, potentially supporting their immune system and overall health.\r\nPostnatal Rejuvenation: These granules may assist in the recovery and rejuvenation of new mothers after childbirth, helping them regain strength and vitality. This may help speed up healing and replenish energy levels during the demanding postpartum period.\r\nHormonal Balance: These granules might help maintain hormonal balance during the postnatal period, which is crucial for lactation and overall well-being. Balanced hormones may contribute to improved emotional health and smoother breastfeeding.\r\nDigestive Support: This granule may help nursing mothers digest food, which benefits both mother and baby. This granule might help ensure better nutrient absorption and comfort during breastfeeding by supporting healthy digestion.\r\nNutritional Enhancement: The granules might help provide essential nutrients to support maternal health during breastfeeding. This could assist in meeting the increased nutritional demands of new mothers, contributing to overall well-being and vitality.', '2 teaspoons twice daily with warm milk or water or as as directed by a healthcare provider.\r\nMix well and consume immediately. ', 'Consult a healthcare professional before use, especially if pregnant, nursing, or on other medications.\r\nDo not exceed the recommended dosage.\r\nDiscontinue use and consult a doctor if any adverse reactions occur.\r\nStore in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight; always check the expiry date before consumption.', 'Good to Know:Flavour:- Elaichi (Cardamom);This granule contains natural ingredients traditionally used for lactation support;Suitable for breastfeeding mothers seeking to enhance lactation\r\nQuick Tips:For best results, consume consistently and maintain a balanced diet\r\nConcerns 