(6, 'Softovac Sf Powder 250gm', 'Softovac SF Powder is a sugar-free laxative used to relieve constipation and support healthy digestion. It softens stools, improves bowel movement, and helps cleanse the digestive system. Made with natural ingredients like Isabgol and herbs, it promotes regularity without causing dependency and helps maintain overall digestive health.', 369.15, 'Health Conditions', 22, '693103810f93f_softovac_sf_1.jpeg', '2025-11-14 03:27:09', 'Digestive Care', 'Lupin Ltd', 49.19, 25, '[\"It contains natural ingredients.\\r\",\"Provides effective relief from constipation.\\r\",\"The powder is sugar-free and non-habit forming.\\r\",\"Helps activate the secretion of digestive juices.\\r\",\"It contains ingredients with laxative properties and benefits for indigestion.\"]', 'Cassia Fistula ( Aragvadha ) (0.2 Gm) + Hemej Terminalia Chebula (0.3 Gm) + Isabgol (3.5 Gm) + Mulethi Glycyrrhiza Glabra (0.25 Gm) + Saunf Foeniculum Vulgare (0.25 Gm) + Sonamukhi (0.15 Gm)', 'Regulates Bowel Function: The powder contains natural Ayurvedic ingredients that help regulate bowel movements and maintain digestive health.\r\nNon-Addictive Formula: It can provide effective relief from constipation without causing dependency.\r\nSugar-Free: It is suitable for those who need to avoid sugar, such as persons with imbalanced blood sugar levels.\r\nActivates Digestive Juices: It helps stimulate the secretion of digestive juices to enhance digestion.\r\nFacilitates Bowel Movement: It contains Sonamukhi and Amaltas, which have properties that help in the smooth evacuation of stools.\r\nImproves Indigestion Symptoms: Saunf helps manage flatulence and improve symptoms of indigestion.', 'Dosage: Adult- 1-2 teaspoonfuls (5-10 g) followed by a glass of lukewarm water at bedtime or as recommeneded by your physician.', 'For oral consumption only.\r\nKeep out of reach of children.\r\nStore in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.\r\nConsult a healthcare professional before use if you are pregnant, nursing, or have any pre-existing medical conditions.\r\nIf any adverse reactions occur, discontinue use and consult a healthcare professional.', 'Good to Know:Softovac SF Powder is a natural and effective remedy for managing constipation and maintaining digestive health without causing dependency;It has a high-fibre formula enriched with natural actives\r\nQuick Tips:Drink plenty of water throughout the day to enhance the effects of the product and maintain hydration;Include lots of fibre like green leafy vegetables in your diet to support regular bowel movements\r\nAllergy Information:It contains sodium benzoate. Consult a healthcare professional if you have concerns about allergic reactions\r\nConcerns It Can Help With:Constipation;Stomach discomfort;Irregular bowel movements;Frequency of product usage;Use daily or as directed by a healthcare professional.\r\nOther Information:Product Form:- Powder', '[\"What is Softovac SF Powder used for?:Softovac SF Powder is used for regulating bowel function, relieving constipation, and improving digestion with natural ayurvedic ingredients.\\r\",\"How does Softovac SF Powder work?:The powder contains ingredients like Isabgol and Sonamukhi that help soften stools and promote regular bowel movements, while other ingredients like Amaltas and Saunf help improve digestion and manage flatulence.\\r\",\"Are there any side effects?:Softovac SF Powder is generally safe for use. However, if you experience any adverse reactions, discontinue use and consult a healthcare professional immediately.\\r\",\"Is Softovac SF Powder suitable for children?:Consult a healthcare professional before using this product for children.\\r\",\"What should I do if I miss a dose?:If you miss a dose, take it as soon as you remember. If it is close to your next dose, skip the missed dose and continue your regular schedule.\\r\",\"Is Softovac SF safe for daily use?:Softovac SF is generally safe for daily use as directed. Long-term use shoul